Catppuccin Flatpak Compatibility

sudo flatpak override flatpak themes to ~/.themes: sudo flatpak override --filesystem=$HOME/.themes
sudo flatpak override flatpak icons to ~/.icons: sudo flatpak override --filesystem=$HOME/.icons
sudo flatpak override flatpak themes to ~/.config/gtk-4.0 locally: flatpak override --user --filesystem=xdg-config/gtk-4.0
sudo flatpak override flatpak themes to ~/.config/gtk-4.0 globally: sudo flatpak override --filesystem=xdg-config/gtk-4.0

